english: Log in to ClubbingOwl with Facebook to see what your friends are up to.
Log in to ClubbingOwl with Facebook to see what <%=first_name?>'s favorite clubs, promoters and guest-lists.
Login to ClubbingOwl with your Facebook account.
german: Anmelden bei ClubbingOwl mit deinem Facebook Profil.

english: Welcome to ClubbingOwl! The  easiest way to join guest-lists and reserve tables at your favorite venues.
german: Willkommen bei ClubbingOwl! Wir sind zur Zeit im beta Modus und werden erst nach und nach mehr Features freischalten. Schaut bitte bald zurueck!

english: ClubbingOwl is the easiest way to join guest-lists and reserve tables at your favorite venues.

ClubbingOwl provides you with the fastest way to plan your evening. Find out where your friends party and join them! With ClubbingOwl being on a guest-list or reserving a table is only one click away! It’s free, try it!
Discovering where your friends are partying has never been easier!
german: Heraus zu finden wo deine Freunde feiern gehen war noch nie einfacherer!

english: ClubbingOwl is the easiest way to join guest-lists and reserve tables at your favorite venues.

english: Discovering where your friends are partying has never been easier!
german: Raus zu finden wo deine Freunde hin Ausgehen war noch nie einfacher!
